Version 0.2

* New profile format:
  * Using separated calibration and scanner profiles
* Wizard: combined laser and platform calibration in one
* New auto check algorithm: check motor direction and pattern and laser detection
* New adjustment workbench:
  * Scan adjustment: separated camera settings for texture and laser detection
  * Calibration adjustment: separated settings for pattern and laser detection
* Added auto check to calibration workbench
* Improved laser detection:
  * Easy to adjust to light conditions
  * Easy to adjust for different object materials, colors, surfaces
* Improved calibration algorithms
* Improved scan algorithm:
  * Using separated camera settings for texture and laser detection
* Improved performance
* Apply point cloud ROI before scanning
* Fixed Clear EEPROM
* New updates system
* Added verbose log file
* Log file management
* Internal refactor
